    slug: 'empowering-young-adults-proactive-digital-footprint-education-career-success',
    title: 'Empowering Young Adults: A Guide to Proactive Digital Footprint Education for Future Career Success',
    category: 'Online Safety',
    excerpt: 'Learn how young adults can proactively manage their digital footprint to enhance career prospects, build a positive online reputation, and achieve professional success.',
