    title: 'Family Scam-Proof Strategy: Proactive Discussions to Identify Evolving Online Threats',
    category: 'Financial Safety',
    excerpt: 'Empower your family against evolving online scams. Learn to build a proactive, shared strategy through open discussions to identify and report new phishing, social engineering, and digital threats.',
    metaDescription: 'Empower your family against evolving online scams. Learn to build a proactive, shared strategy through open discussions to identify and report new phishing, social engineering, and digital threats.',
